        <p>Your data is protected with secure authentication and two-factor authentication options. Your journey, your privacy.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="landing-cta">
      <h2>Ready to Start Your Journey?</h2>
      <p>Join Mahi today and take the first step towards achieving your body goals.</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <%= link_to "Sign Up Free", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
